OL,7,FThe ESRI said the tax cuts, welfare
OL,8,Fincreases, cost-of-living measures and
OL,9,Findirect tax cuts had "grown broadly
OL,10,Fin line" with forecast wage growth of
OL,11,F4.2% for 2025 compared to the 2024
OL,12,Ffinancial package.
OL,14,FBut it added that there are smaller
OL,15,Fgains for middle income households.
