OL,7,FAssociate research professor at the
OL,8,FESRI, Dr Claire Keane, said: "The
OL,9,Fwithdrawal of cost-of-living policies,
OL,10,Fwhich has begun in Budget 2025 with
OL,11,Fthe reduction in energy credits, may
OL,12,Fincrease the number of pensioner and
OL,13,Fdisabled households at-risk-of-poverty
OL,14,Fin the future, unless there is an
OL,15,Faccompanying increase in core welfare
OL,16,Frates."
