OL,5,Ctank
OL,7,FDr Karina Doorley, another associate
OL,8,Fresearch professor at the ESRI, said
OL,9,Fthe budget would have "little effect
OL,10,Fon reducing overall poverty or child
OL,11,Fpoverty".
OL,13,F"The exchequer cost of the untargeted
OL,14,Fcost-of-living measures, such as
OL,15,Fenergy credits and the double child
OL,16,Fbenefit payment, would have been
OL,17,Fenough to finance a second tier of
OL,18,Fchild benefit which could lift 40,000
OL,19,Fchildren out of poverty."
