OL,5,Ctank
OL,7,FESRI research professor Kieran McQuinn
OL,8,Fsaid that from a macroeconomic
OL,9,Fperspective, "the increased levels of
OL,10,Fcapital spending, coupled with the
OL,11,Fenhanced commitment to the investment
OL,12,Ffunds established, does offer the
OL,13,Fpotential to put investment on a more
OL,14,Fsustainable footing in the Irish
OL,15,Feconomy".
OL,17,FThe research said that some elements
OL,18,Fof the tax-benefit system, such as
OL,19,Fchild benefit, the living alone
OL,20,Fallowance and fuel allowance have been
OL,21,F"frozen" in nominal terms.
